parameters:
Noah's leg had deteriorated further than before, with the necrosis
progressing.

Noah, whose life could end at any moment, was not a surprising
sight...
That night, Luuna and Noah talked in the park.
That night, Luuna and Noah talked in the park.
That night, Luuna and Noah talked in the park.

Cain: Luuna, Becky, are you really going? Even Noah and Pole are
coming along.
Becky: I'll definitely defeat Lucia. That black witch.

Becky: The "Knights of Messiah" from the Kingdom of Moduna didn't come
to help us though.

Luuna: Yes, the "Knights of Messiah" from the Kingdom of Moduna on the
surface. They're a knightly order that helps other countries. I sent a
letter asking for support to their leader, Lord Ceres, but we were
refused.

Luuna: Can't be helped. The opponent is the direct-line mage Lucia.
The power of a direct-line mage is different from that of a normal
mage, they possess an incomparable amount of magical power.
Luuna: But we can't just let Lucia's tyranny continue any longer.

Dalieh: Geez, if the village chief's father heard about this, he'd be
furious. Forming a rebel army on your own and challenging the royal
capital Jupiterino. There's no way you can win against Lucia.

Cain: Big brother, keep it a secret from father, okay? We'll be the
ones getting scolded.
Dalieh: But before you go, Luuna, can I hear 'that answer'?
Luuna: At a time like this...

Dalieh: You see, I want Luuna to be my girlfriend. I have many
lovers... no, girlfriends prepared by my father, but I prefer pure
girls like Luuna.

Cain: Geez... It's funny to hear playboy big brother talk about having
a girlfriend. You just want to make Luuna another one of your sex
friends, right?

Cain: Because your love arrows don't work on Luuna, you're interested
in her, right? We brothers are the sons of the village chief, so most
girls listen to what we say, but Luuna won't nod along.

Dalieh: That's right. Luuna has her childhood friend Noah after all.
Luuna, if you break up with that poor Noah and become my girlfriend,
you can indulge in as much luxury as you want?

Luuna: Dalieh, I'm sorry. To be honest, I don't find you attractive as
a member of the opposite sex...
Noah: Dalieh, stop it! You're troubling Luuna.

Dalieh: Noah, you're just a childhood friend of Luuna's. It's cheeky
for you to butt in like this.

Noah: No, I've been meaning to tell Dalieh directly for a while now.
He's the son of the village chief and he's been messing around with
various girls, causing them trouble. Now he's targeting Luuna.

Noah: Let me make it clear, Dalieh. Both Luuna and I dislike 'flashy
men' like you!

Dalieh: Sigh... It's pitiful for Luuna to be with a poor man with no
experience with women like you.

Dalieh: Noah, just watch? I'll definitely make Luuna my woman? I'll
make her squeal with my technique. All females are the same after all.

Noah: Too bad for you. Luuna dislikes flashy men who make women cry
like you do. Isn't that right, Luuna?

Dalieh: Hmph... Luuna, you'll understand soon enough. Who between Noah
and me... is the superior male?

Becky: Sigh... Dalieh is the same as ever. He hits on any cute girl he
sees. I'm glad I got married to Pole early.

Pole: Heheh, I'm a lucky guy to have a cute woman like Becky as my
wife. Right, Becky? You love me, don't you?
Becky: Pole, don't say embarrassing things in front of others.

Becky: Anyway, we're going to launch a surprise attack on the fortress
in the imperial capital Jupiterino and defeat Lucia. We can't stand
Lucia's tyranny any longer. Keep what happens from now on a secret
from the village chief.
Cain: Got it. Well, do your best out there.

Luuna: Don't worry. If it gets dangerous, we'll escape. Well then...
I'm off now.

Luuna and the resistance head towards the fortress in the Jupiterino
Kingdom. There, Princess Lucia and the generals of the allied Valentia
Kingdom had gathered.
